headline: Piper Sandler Raises PT on ConocoPhillips (COP), Keeps an Overweight Rating
summary: ConocoPhillips (NYSE:COP) is one of the Most Undervalued US Stocks According to Wall Street Analysts. On August 18, Piper Sandler raised the firm’s price target on ConocoPhillips (NYSE:COP) from $123 to $124, while keeping an Overweight rating on the stock. The firm noted that the company showed resilience in its fiscal second quarter of 2025. […]
